Even as dungeons go in this game the ramp up of loot in them is just screwed up.  That is why so few low/mid level players go into the dungeons ment for them.  The loot just isn't worth the risk.  A level 30 can get the cougar claw earring in a nice safe outdoor area, but you can't get something as good in solA.  It just doesn't make sense, they need to upgrade the loot in the mid range dungeons.<br>
<br>
